– ORM & Community Management.

Online Reputation Management (ORM) and Community Management services are vital in this day and age. ORM is the process of monitoring, managing, and repairing a company or individual’s online reputation. Community Management is the process of cultivating, managing, and moderating an online community around a product, brand, or service. Both ORM and Community Management are necessary in order to protect and grow a company’s or individual’s online presence. 

